  <!-- GETTING STARTED -->
  <h2>ðŸš€ Getting Started</h2>
  <h3>Prerequisites</h3>
  <p>Python 3.8+ and pip installed on your machine.</p>

  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="step-title">Clone the repository</div>
        <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/your-username/devsearch.git
cd devsearch</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="step-title">Create and activate a virtual environment</div>
        <pre><code># Windows
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate

# macOS / Linux
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="step-title">Install dependencies</div>
        <pre><code>pip install -r requirements.txt</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">4</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="step-title">Apply migrations</div>
        <pre><code>python manage.py migrate</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">5</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="step-title">Create a superuser (admin)</div>
        <pre><code>python manage.py createsuperuser</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">6</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="step-title">Run the development server</div>
        <pre><code>python manage.py runserver</code></pre>
        <p style="margin-top:8px;">Visit <code>http://localhost:8000</code> in your browser.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
